# Arduino-Based Smart Dustbin 🚮

This project is a smart dustbin that automatically opens its lid when an object is detected nearby.

## Components Used
- Arduino Nano
- Ultrasonic Sensor (HC-SR04)
- Servo Motor
- Jumper Wires

## Working Principle
The ultrasonic sensor measures distance.  
When an object comes within a preset range, the servo motor opens the dustbin lid automatically.

## Applications
- Touchless waste management
- Hygiene-focused environments

